text: Andheri East constituency is one of the 26 Vidhan Sabha constituencies located in Mumbai Suburban district. Andheri East is part of the Mumbai North West Lok Sabha constituency along with five other Vidhan Sabha segments, namely Goregaon, Versova, Jogeshwari East, Dindoshi and Andheri West in Mumbai Suburban district. ==Members of Legislative Assembly== Key {| class="wikitable" |- !colspan="2"|Election!!Member!!Party |- |style="background-color: " | | 2009 | Suresh Shetty | Indian National Congress |- |style="background-color: " | | 2014 | Ramesh Latke | Shiv Sena |- |style="background-color: " | | 2019 | Ramesh Latke | Shiv Sena |} ==Election results== ===Assembly elections 2009=== ===Assembly elections 2014=== ==References== Category:Assembly constituencies of Mumbai Category:Assembly constituencies of Maharashtra Category:Politics of Mumbai Suburban district
